The,UK,Biodiversity,Action,Reporting,System,BARS,supports,the,conservation,community,by,providing,a,place,for,people,to,post,and,search,for,information,on,work,being,done,to,benefit,important,habitats,and,species,This,information,includes,the,level,of,activity,where,it,is,taking,place,and,the,project,s,goals,BARS,also,maps,action,locations,and,produces,statistical,summaries,of,the,data,The,goals,of,the,system,are,to,help,committees,coordinate,their,actions,and,to,help,government,agencies,report,on,biodiversity,loss,prevention,work,for,their,various,commitments,and,treaties,Developer,can,access,and,display,BARS,data,using,SOAP,calls,issued,in,XML,format